## ï¿½ï¿½ Notes:
- Replace `organizations`, `users`, `cases` with your actual table names
- Add query parameters like `?limit=10` to limit results
- Use `?select=column1,column2` to select specific columns
- Add filters with `?column=eq.value` for equality filters

These commands will help you test your Supabase connection and query your database directly from the terminal!
